  fhir:DomainResource.text [
     fhir:Narrative.status [ fhir:value "extensions" ] ;
     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: ValueSet Kemoterapiregime</b></p><a name=\"Kemoterapiregime\"> </a><a name=\"hcKemoterapiregime\"> </a><p>This value set includes codes based on the following rules:</p><ul><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"CodeSystem-SKS.html\"><code>https://kip.rkkp.dk/fhir/CodeSystem/SKS</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated, which means it is fixed to the version provided in this specification\"> version ?2.23.1</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-SKS.html#SKS-BWHA167\">BWHA167</a></td><td>ABVD</td><td>Behandling med doxyrubicin+bleomycin+vinblastin+dacarbazin (ABVD)</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-SKS.html#SKS-BWHA138\">BWHA138</a></td><td>BeaCOPP</td><td>Behandling med BEACOPP</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-SKS.html#SKS-BWHA310\">BWHA310</a></td><td>BEAM</td><td>Behandling med BEAM (konditionering)</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-SKS.html#SKS-BWHA165\">BWHA165</a></td><td>CHOEP</td><td>Behandling med cyclophosphamid+doxorubicin+vinkristin+etoposid+prednisolon (CHOEP)</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-SKS.html#SKS-BWHA119\">BWHA119</a></td><td>CHOP</td><td>Behandling med cyclophosphamid+doxorubicin+vinkristin+prednisolon (CHOP)</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-SKS.html#SKS-BWHA166\">BWHA166</a></td><td>CNOP</td><td>Behandling med cyclophosphamid+mitoxantron+vinkristin+prednisolon (CNOP)</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-SKS.html#SKS-BWHA134\">BWHA134</a></td><td>COP</td><td>Behandling med cyclophosphamid+vinkristin+prednisolon (CVP) (COP)</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-SKS.html#SKS-BWHA168\">BWHA168</a></td><td>LVPP</td><td>Behandling med klorambucil+vinblastin+procarbazin+prednisolon (LVPP)</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-SKS.html#SKS-BWHA258\">BWHA258</a>